msgid ""
"<strong>Warning:</strong> To capture the amount manually, you also need to set\n"
"                    the Capture Delay to manual on your Adyen account settings."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຄຳເຕືອນ:</strong> ເພື່ອຕັດເງິນດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ, ທ່ານຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງຕັ້ງຄ່າ\n"
"                    Capture Delay ເປັນ manual ໃນການຕັ້ງຄ່າບັນຊີ Adyen ຂອງທ່ານ."

